            <h2><strong>Delivery Information</strong></h2>
            <p>
                At KidsShop, we aim to provide a seamless and efficient delivery experience for our valued customers. Please review the following delivery information:
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Shipping Methods</strong></h3>
            <p>
                We offer a variety of shipping options tailored to your needs. Choose from standard shipping, express delivery, and expedited shipping. Delivery times and fees may vary depending on the selected shipping method and your location.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Order Processing</strong></h3>
            <p>
                Once an order is placed, our team works diligently to process and fulfill it promptly. Order processing times typically range from 1 to 3 business days. Please note that processing times may be longer during peak seasons or due to unforeseen circumstances.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Shipping Costs</strong></h3>
            <p>
                Shipping costs are calculated based on the selected shipping method, the total weight of the package, and the destination address. Free shipping is available on orders above a specified amount, subject to terms and conditions.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Delivery Times</strong></h3>
            <p>
                Estimated delivery times vary based on the shipping method selected and the destination address. Standard shipping usually takes 5-7 business days, while express delivery ensures delivery within 1-2 business days. Actual delivery times may vary due to external factors.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>International Shipping</strong></h3>
            <p>
                We offer international shipping to select countries. International orders may be subject to customs clearance procedures and import duties, which are the responsibility of the recipient.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Tracking Orders</strong></h3>
            <p>
                Once your order is dispatched, you will receive a tracking number via email to track your package's journey until it reaches your doorstep.
            </p>

